{"tid":1787901,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鄭錦滿：理大廚房佬亦已經成功聯絡上張超雄議員 故此我相信他的人身安全能得到保障","createTime":"2019-12-18T09:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T11:13:41.000Z","uid":81424,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"06c0679675d3508db83dd4ce17e85f6b57e116f6","tid":1787901,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:09:29.000Z","msg":"鄭錦滿：今日我帶同「理大廚房佬」最愛的山崎麵包銅鑼燒，作最後一次探訪。<br />\n<br />\n外面正在抹黑我熱血公民鄭錦滿，「四眼食人血饅頭」！就此，我表示問心無愧，亦不想再添煩添亂。<br />\n<br />\n「理大廚房佬」與我溝通後，已經將本人姓名從探訪名單上剔除，轉為袁師母陳錦美；他亦已經成功聯絡上張超雄議員、黃毓民、杜汶澤喱騷、國難五金、星火同盟抗爭支援、高登討論區新聞部記者爆炸頭等等朋友，故此我相信他的人身安全能得到保障。<br />\n<br />\n如無意外，本周五他會在朋友陪同下出院，感激醫護人員一直以來的包容及悉心照顧，天佑義民！好人一生平安！<br />\n<br />\n註：此帖圖文經「理大廚房佬」細閱後才公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/4eyesbro/photos/a.802024083192921/2704581719603805/?type=3&amp;__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARA5y0FzlEPZNj3YyUdstH8H0-R6Nmzl4X-88VgQ32tFOpdQzVbZv3hH3GvYaBPilcfHXxlyD3QlviA8j9UF_r4Q-Ky-5K91PRmoaAmG7n0FxpjHi-osClZqdGKCMqg6QrkrRrJzZ6D7kPIDJMRlKJ9NTvRHrR6a8ORYV0jmt5ReuuGjJUv4-n_5N81A3Rq1fURhuU_m9zgPmbW9aN7cBA2Hd0xqn-SRFZeVOgaKJ9BJ1H_GBWY4e04pI6T54FR5lLvgv60leISgYWdiZSEHVh-2z2VLYc_ROrcVUqhmL663UXBSigpu3XL6vIP6JguBz0u6tuJ0ZLflkLsXejZpvsJajw&amp;__tn__=H-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F4eyesbro%2Fphotos%2Fa.802024083192921%2F2704581719603805%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26__xts__%255B0%255D%3D68.ARA5y0FzlEPZNj3YyUdstH8H0-R6Nmzl4X-88VgQ32tFOpdQzVbZv3hH3GvYaBPilcfHXxlyD3QlviA8j9UF_r4Q-Ky-5K91PRmoaAmG7n0FxpjHi-osClZqdGKCMqg6QrkrRrJzZ6D7kPIDJMRlKJ9NTvRHrR6a8ORYV0jmt5ReuuGjJUv4-n_5N81A3Rq1fURhuU_m9zgPmbW9aN7cBA2Hd0xqn-SRFZeVOgaKJ9BJ1H_GBWY4e04pI6T54FR5lLvgv60leISgYWdiZSEHVh-2z2VLYc_ROrcVUqhmL663UXBSigpu3XL6vIP6JguBz0u6tuJ0ZLflkLsXejZpvsJajw%26__tn__%3DH-R&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BupKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=6587d44c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/4eyesbro/photos/a.802024083192921/2704581719603805/?type=3&amp;__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARA5y0FzlEPZNj3YyUdstH8H0-R6Nmzl4X-88VgQ32tFOpdQzVbZv3hH3GvYaB